                                        <h2>Welcome to Charket!</h2>
                                        <p class="overview">Built for marketing, Charket connects Salesforce, the world’s #1 CRM application, with WeChat, one of the most popular social platforms. By using Charket, marketing people can generate QR codes for marketing campaigns and collect lead information from WeChat users who scan the QR codes. All leads are automatically put under marketing campaigns and centrally managed within Salesforce.
                                        <br/>
                                        Here are steps to complete the setup of Charket and use Charket with marketing campaigns. Click the link of each step in the sidebar for more information.
                                        </p>
