                                                <li>
                                                    <a href="#menu" role="tab" data-toggle="tab" id="menu_link">Customize WeChat Menu</a>: create a WeChat menu from within Salesforce
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <a href="#material" role="tab" data-toggle="tab" id="material_link">Add Message Templates</a>: define the templates of messages to be sent to WeChat subscribers. A template can be used for the following scenarios:
                                                    <ul>
                                                        <li>
                                                            Send a greeting message to new WeChat subscribers.
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            Send a greeting message to WeChat users who scan your QR code.
                                                        </li>
                                                        <li>
                                                            Send auto responses to messages from WeChat subscribers or to menu actions by WeChat subscribers.
                                                        </li>

                                                    </ul>
                                                </li>
                                                <li>
                                                    <a href="#message" role="tab" data-toggle="tab" id="message_link">Create Messages</a>: create messages using the templates defined in the above step.
                                                </li>
                                            </ul>
                                        </p>
                                        <p class="steptitle"> 
